  VALUES ?language {wd:Q5287}.
} If you're only interested in Japanese and Spanish, subquery %0 should be SELECT DISTINCT ?language {
  VALUES ?language {
    wd:Q5287
    wd:Q1321
  }.
} If you're only interested in languages that are used in countries located in Asia, subquery %0 should be """@en;
